conversations.content:
It’s clear and keeps the mystery, which adds charm to your style — but if you think Dimas might actually be confused or not engage with it, adding a subtle hint could make it more enticing. For example:

> Crack it and you’ll earn ultimate bragging rights (and possibly discover my questionable taste in snacks);

This keeps your playful tone but gives a small nudge toward what the bonus might be, sparking curiosity without spoiling the surprise.
